articles.title: Who stunned our judges with their Miami Grand Prix efforts? - Formula 1
articles.description: Formula 1 went from one Sprint to another with a thrilling weekend of action around the Miami International Autodrome, but which drivers impressed our Power Rankings judges and made the top half of the charts? Check out the latest scores below.
articles.content: Fernando Alonso came to blows with team mate Lance Stroll at the start of the Sprint and could only manage 15th in qualifying, four spots behind the Canadian, but the two-time champion made up for it… [+504 chars]
